Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.62,0:02:05.45,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:121622,125459}No matter how one looks at it, Maya Kitajima is an average girl…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.45,0:02:10.25,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:125459,130255}…but, in her heart, there is a burning desire to become an actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.25,0:02:14.42,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:130255,134426}Maya, whose talent was discovered by\Na former actress, Tsukikage Chigusa…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.42,0:02:19.76,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:134426,139765}…is determined to follow in her footsteps by becoming an actress in Tsukikage Theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.76,0:02:26.77,Episode title,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:140766,146772}{\an5\pos(766,750)\fscy95\blur1\fad(200,0)}—Episode 02—\NMr. Purple Rose
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.89,0:02:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:147898,152819}{\i1}Dear Mom, I am now a live-in student at Theater Tsukikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.81,0:02:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:152819,155656}{\i1}Sorry I left without notifying you…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.65,0:02:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:155656,157656}{\i1}…but I'm doing fine here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.75,0:02:50.25,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:168752,170253}Manpuku Ken
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.37,0:02:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:170379,172422}I'm sorry, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.42,0:02:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:172422,176426}But I really want to become an actress by any means.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.30,0:03:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:178303,182849}{\i1}Now I'm going to junior high school from here…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.84,0:03:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:182849,186228}{\i1}…and I am getting a scholarship for this school…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.93,0:03:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:187938,191024}{\i1}…so don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.32,0:03:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:199324,200325}Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.32,0:03:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:200325,202411}What's going on?\NWaking us all up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.16,0:03:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:205163,207791}What time do you think it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.79,0:03:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:207791,210669}I have to get up at 6 tomorrow for my duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.66,0:03:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:210669,212504}Let me sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.54,0:03:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:213547,215132}I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.88,0:03:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:215882,218051}On that note, let's get back to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.59,0:03:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:219594,224558}{\i1}My four roommates are all\Ndrama girls" from all over the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.22,0:03:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:226226,227978}{\i1}Mina.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.97,0:03:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:227978,230105}{\i1}Taiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.10,0:03:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:230105,231440}{\i1}Sayaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.44,0:03:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:231440,233233}{\i1}And Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.23,0:03:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:233233,234317}{\i1}She's so handsome.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.31,0:03:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:234317,238196}{\i1}But she's a girl without a flaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.32,0:04:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:242325,245328}{\i1}And, Mom, don't be surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.32,0:04:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:245328,249791}{\i1}I was chosen to play Beth in "Little Women".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.71,0:04:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:251710,257215}{\i1}Tsukikage Theater's first performance, part advertisement as well as opening the theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.21,0:04:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:257215,259634}{\i1}I'll play Beth on that stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.38,0:04:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:261386,264264}Shoot, I slept in!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.26,0:04:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:264264,266433}Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.43,0:04:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:266433,268810}Sorry, but I'm running late!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.81,0:04:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:268810,269936}I'll see you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.89,0:04:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:272898,274107}– Ms. Maya.\N– Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.10,0:04:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:274107,276443}You dropped something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.44,0:04:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:276443,278278}Oh, that's a letter to my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.27,0:04:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:278278,280822}I can mail it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.82,0:04:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:280822,282240}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.24,0:04:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:282240,283825}Bye now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.03,0:04:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:288038,289873}Oh, Madame, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.83,0:04:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:290832,291792}That is?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.45,0:04:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:292459,294211}Oh, Ms. Maya's letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.21,0:04:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:294211,295545}I'll take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.54,0:04:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:295545,296379}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.54,0:04:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:297547,299674}She has left her home to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.67,0:05:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:300675,302052}Madame…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.81,0:05:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:310811,314231}{\i1}What she needs now is to forget her past.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.65,0:05:26.91,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:322656,326910}With the performance date coming close,\Nthey progressed with their practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.82,0:05:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:327828,329204}Maya!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.20,0:05:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:329204,331373}Look how you are picking it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.37,0:05:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:331373,336419}Are you trying to understand how Beth would like to pick it up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.75,0:05:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:337754,339339}There she goes again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.33,0:05:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:339339,343134}It's impossible for her to play Beth,\Nbeing a total amateur.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.13,0:05:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:343134,345887}Sayaka would fit Beth much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.88,0:05:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:345887,349140}I think Maya's just a teacher's pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.55,0:05:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:350559,351643}Emotions!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.64,0:05:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:351643,354229}Emotions will make the play.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.22,0:05:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:354229,355647}Emotions…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.64,0:05:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:356648,359192}Let's play it again from the piano scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.19,0:06:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:359192,360902}Jo. Meg.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.90,0:06:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:360902,362362}Beth, play the piano.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.36,0:06:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:362362,363780}Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.07,0:06:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:369077,371246}No!\NThat's not Beth playing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.24,0:06:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:371246,372706}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.70,0:06:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:372706,374374}Try again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.75,0:06:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:375750,377502}No!\NTry again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.50,0:06:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:377502,378628}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.46,0:06:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:386469,388054}Here you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.18,0:06:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:389180,391099}Thanks for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.26,0:06:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:394269,396521}I'm no good at all…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.52,0:06:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:396521,397856}What are you not good at?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.94,0:06:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:398940,401276}You… are from Ondine Theater!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.27,0:06:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:401276,404863}Sakurakōji Yū.\NNice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.86,0:06:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:404863,407407}I'm Kitajima Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.40,0:06:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:407407,410619}Oh, I'm helping them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.61,0:06:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:410619,412996}Oh, you're helping this store.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.04,0:06:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:415040,418543}Hmm, you enrolled in Tsukikage Theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.75,0:07:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:425759,427677}Everyone is like that\Nwhen you start out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.67,0:07:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:427677,431181}I still get corrected all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.18,0:07:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:431181,433850}Here it is.\NCome in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.64,0:07:13.64,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:431640,433642}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.85,0:07:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:433850,435268}B-But…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.26,0:07:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:435268,436811}It's okay, come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.81,0:07:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:436811,439064}You want to play Beth better, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.77,0:07:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:444778,447113}Yeah, raise your hands up a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.78,0:07:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:449783,450825}Come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.03,0:07:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:452035,453787}Here is some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.78,0:07:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:453787,454663}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.66,0:07:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:454663,455872}It's not time for tea yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.87,0:07:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:455872,457457}We have to practice!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.45,0:07:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:457457,460001}Oh no, what a strict teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.50,0:07:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:465507,469803}Miss Tsukikage has sold all her jewels.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.80,0:07:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:469803,472013}She is trying to sell her house in Yokohama, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.01,0:07:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:472013,474182}I see.\NThanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.81,0:08:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:485819,488989}Your mom is so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.98,0:08:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:488989,489739}Yeah, she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.41,0:08:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:500417,501876}Mother…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.87,0:08:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:501876,502752}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.75,0:08:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:502752,504671}Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.67,0:08:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:504671,507716}Oh, this is fine here.\NThank you for the piano lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.71,0:08:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:507716,509634}I think I can try again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.63,0:08:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:509634,510593}Maya…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.59,0:08:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:510593,511720}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.72,0:08:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:511720,514514}…I hope we can play together one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.81,0:08:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:518810,521479}I'll try hard till that day!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.47,0:08:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:521479,522897}Good bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.48,0:08:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:530488,535285}Well, I sure hope that you will produce a star soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.28,0:08:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:535285,537912}Until then, let's see how\Nmany money trees grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.20,0:09:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:539205,542083}Well the, good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.08,0:09:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:542083,543877}I'll see you again soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.87,0:09:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:543877,547172}I'll come by again, real soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.17,0:09:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:547172,549632}Okay then, bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.02,0:09:31.98,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:569027,571988}Tsukikage Theater
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.37,0:09:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:580371,581623}Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.62,0:09:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:581623,583875}It's me.\NMay I come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.29,0:09:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:585293,590298}I saw Mr. Aoyagi's car outside,\Nso I waited it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.55,0:09:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:592550,596763}The owner of this theater is Mr. Aoyagi, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.76,0:09:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:596763,598807}What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.80,0:10:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:598807,601142}There's only one thing I came here for.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.14,0:10:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:601142,606773}I have no intention to sell the play rights for "The Crimson Goddess."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.77,0:10:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:608775,612737}I will come back again and again\Ntill you change your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.73,0:10:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:613738,615782}Please go home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.78,0:10:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:615782,617325}I'm a little tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.32,0:10:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:617325,620495}I see.\NI won't bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.49,0:10:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:620495,622747}But let me say one thing before I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.74,0:10:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:622747,626543}I wouldn't recommend you signing up with Aoyagi Productions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.54,0:10:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:626543,631840}And sign up with your Metropolitan Entertainment instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.84,0:10:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:631840,633383}No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.38,0:10:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:633383,636219}I will run my theater just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.21,0:10:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:636219,639681}Don't you see that you are being used by Mr. Aoyagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.68,0:10:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:639681,640974}Please go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.97,0:10:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:640974,643017}You have no right to comment like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.01,0:10:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:643017,643977}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.97,0:10:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:643977,649816}But now that I know that the notorious Aoyagi Productions is behind Tsukikage Theater…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.81,0:10:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:649816,652527}…I won't just let this pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.52,0:10:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:652527,654863}Are you threatening me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.86,0:10:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:654863,656531}No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.53,0:10:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:656531,658700}I just want to protect\N"The Crimson Goddess".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.70,0:11:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:658700,660034}Please leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.45,0:11:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:661452,663496}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.88,0:11:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:672881,675507}Please don't harass my teacher like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.63,0:11:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:677635,679846}I don't like anyone who harasses her!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.31,0:11:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:690315,691482}I don't like…!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.53,0:11:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:702535,705496}Beth, Beth, look at me!\NDon't die on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.49,0:11:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:706497,708499}I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.49,0:11:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:708499,711211}Jo, don't let anyone come near me—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.21,0:11:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:711211,713046}No good, Maya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.08,0:11:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:714088,719385}This is the scene where Beth is still thinking of her sisters, even though she's struggling herself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.38,0:12:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:719385,722931}It's been three hours since we first started this same scene…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.93,0:12:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:722931,726351}Think how a sick person\Nwould breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.35,0:12:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:726351,732065}This scene is where Beth is on the edge of her life, and it is this drama's climax.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.06,0:12:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:732065,734400}Get serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.40,0:12:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:734400,736819}Sayaka, let's practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.81,0:12:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:736819,738655}You play Beth as a substitute.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.65,0:12:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:738655,739405}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.40,0:12:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:739405,743034}Maya, go rest and practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.03,0:12:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:743034,744953}Sayaka, get into the bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.95,0:12:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:744953,747038}Then Jo, open the door and enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.03,0:12:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:747038,747914}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.87,0:12:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:749874,752961}Beth, Beth, look at me!\NDon't die on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.96,0:12:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:752961,754462}I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.46,0:12:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:754462,759384}Jo, don't let anyone come near me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.51,0:12:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:760510,763471}{\i1}Sayaka, you play Beth as a substitute.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.10,0:12:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:770103,771312}I don't understand…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.93,0:12:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:772939,777277}I try my hardest\Nto feel like I'm Beth…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.19,0:13:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:778194,780321}I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.32,0:13:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:780321,781864}I don't understand…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.86,0:13:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:781864,784450}Maya, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.45,0:13:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:784450,786995}I don't understand what I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.99,0:13:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:786995,788538}I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.53,0:13:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:788538,789706}You can't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.70,0:13:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:789706,792208}A healthy girl like you\Nis trying to play sick Beth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.08,0:13:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:794085,796796}Of course it takes time to practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.10,0:13:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:815106,816357}{\i1}Three days left.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.35,0:13:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:816357,819027}{\i1}I have to get the role back by any means.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.02,0:13:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:819027,821571}Sayaka, you play Beth as a substitute.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.57,0:13:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:821571,822530}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.07,0:13:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:826075,827785}Hey, girl, get on your feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.78,0:13:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:827785,830455}You'll catch a cold walking\Nlike that in the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.42,0:14:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:839422,843176}{\i1}Three days left till the performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.17,0:14:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:843176,845762}{\i1}Healthy Maya is playing sick Beth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.76,0:14:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:845762,847597}{\i1}It just won't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.59,0:14:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:847597,849349}{\i1}Hey, you'll catch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.39,0:14:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:851392,855313}Yes… rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.31,0:14:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:855313,856898}Rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.64,0:14:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:858649,864405}{\i1}This cold rain can teach me\Nhow to play Beth!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.11,0:14:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:867116,869160}Teacher, she's not back yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.16,0:14:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:869160,872663}What happened to her\Nthat she's not back this late?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.66,0:14:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:872663,876376}Should we call her mother\Nin Yokohama?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.37,0:14:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:876376,878211}There's no need for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.21,0:14:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:878211,883007}She's not the kind of girl who goes home\Njust because she gets scolded.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.76,0:14:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:885760,887470}Teacher…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.47,0:14:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:887470,889472}You all go ahead and go to bed now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.43,0:14:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:892433,895436}It got pretty late before we knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.43,0:14:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:895436,896938}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.45,0:15:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:917458,918418}Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.96,0:15:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:924966,926509}Sorry, but wait for me for a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.50,0:15:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:926509,927635}O-Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.43,0:15:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:932432,933683}That's her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.10,0:15:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:938104,941065}You!\NWhat are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.23,0:15:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:942233,946362}You… Mr. Laurence.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.36,0:15:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:946362,948656}Laurence?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.65,0:15:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:948656,951909}What are you talking about?\NIt's me, Hayami!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.90,0:15:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:951909,955371}Mister, thank you for the music.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.37,0:15:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:955371,957373}What happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.16,0:16:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:961169,962127}Hey?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.83,0:16:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:963838,965673}Hey, get a grip!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.67,0:16:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:965673,966966}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.96,0:16:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:966966,967967}Hey?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.50,0:16:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:968509,969844}{\i1}Mister Laurence?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.84,0:16:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:969844,971053}{\i1}Music?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.97,0:16:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:971971,973848}{\i1}"Little Women"!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.18,0:16:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:980188,982398}She has a high fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.39,0:16:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:982398,985985}I gave her a shot,\Nso let her rest for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.98,0:16:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:985985,987904}Maya, hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.90,0:16:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:987904,988946}Maya…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.90,0:16:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:992909,993910}Maya!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.07,0:16:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:995077,1000249}I'm fine, Jo.\NDon't let anyone come near me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.24,0:16:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1000249,1003586}Maya, that's Beth's words…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.58,0:16:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1003586,1005254}She's becoming Beth herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.63,0:16:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1013638,1015723}{\i1}With that high of a fever…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.01,0:16:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1017016,1018684}{\i1}…will she be able to get on the stage?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.49,0:17:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1035493,1042375}Welcome to "Little Women",\Nthe first play of Tsukikage Theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.33,0:17:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1043334,1044085}{\i1}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.25,0:17:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1046254,1048130}{\i1}The Himekawa family…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.13,0:17:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1048130,1050216}{\i1}…Hayami Masumi and Onodera…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.21,0:17:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1050216,1053052}{\i1}…and critics in the middle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.05,0:17:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1053052,1054136}{\i1}Something's fishy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.97,0:17:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1054971,1059559}Please enjoy our play till the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.77,0:17:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1063771,1068859}You did a great job getting\Nthis many critics and reporters.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.85,0:17:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1068859,1073072}Teacher, Maya…\Nhas a fever of 40°C.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.07,0:17:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1073072,1074532}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.40,0:17:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1075408,1078494}There's no way\Nshe can be on the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.49,0:18:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1078494,1081289}Teacher, I can play as a substitute.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.16,0:18:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1086168,1088796}Maya, what are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.79,0:18:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1088796,1091591}I can do it.\NI can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.59,0:18:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1091591,1093843}What if you pass out on stage?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.84,0:18:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1093843,1095136}I'll get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.13,0:18:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1095136,1097096}Please let me play!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.09,0:18:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1097096,1099807}I see. Go on.\NTry your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.80,0:18:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1099807,1101726}But Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.72,0:18:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1101726,1103352}It's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.35,0:18:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1103352,1105813}Maya, Maya.\NCan you stand up?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.85,0:18:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1108858,1112153}Maya, are you still going to play?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.24,0:18:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1118242,1120620}I am… Beth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.58,0:18:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1128586,1133007}Before mother comes home,\Nlet's think of a Christmas present for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.00,0:18:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1133007,1137303}I'm thinking of something for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.30,0:19:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1137303,1141599}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.30,0:18:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1137303,1139722}Maya…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.72,0:19:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1139722,1141599}…what a determined person you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.81,0:19:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1144810,1147104}Hey, Sakurakōji.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.10,0:19:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1147104,1149315}Oh, Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.31,0:19:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1149315,1152610}This play of Tsukikage Theater\Nisn't all that great.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.61,0:19:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1152610,1156572}Especially Beth. She's slow in her motion and her speech. She's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.82,0:19:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1157823,1160242}She can't help it.\NShe has a fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.24,0:19:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1160242,1161911}Fever?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.91,0:19:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1161911,1166374}She's on stage with\Na fever of 40°C.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.37,0:19:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1166374,1168709}40°C?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.70,0:19:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1168709,1172129}Oh yes, I have something good for Mother's present
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.12,0:19:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1172129,1173881}I'll go get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.97,0:19:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1180971,1183599}Maya, your speech is slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.59,0:19:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1183599,1186602}Sorry, I can't focus very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.60,0:19:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1186602,1189230}No excuse is useful here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.23,0:19:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1189230,1192024}Stand up!\NYour turn again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.02,0:19:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1192024,1193317}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.49,0:20:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1202493,1204036}Here, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.54,0:20:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1207540,1211585}Oh, did anything funny happen\Nwhile I was gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.58,0:20:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1211585,1215464}Sisters, share the story with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.17,0:20:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1216173,1218092}Oh, here comes Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.09,0:20:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1218092,1221220}What did you all do today?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.80,0:20:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1221804,1229228}{\i1}A fever of 40°C and she grows even more beautiful as the play goes on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.22,0:20:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1229228,1234191}May I help give out present for poor kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.19,0:20:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1234191,1236819}No, I really want to help!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.69,0:20:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1238696,1241490}{\i1}Where in that small body…?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.49,0:20:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1241490,1243617}{\i1}Where is the magical power hidden?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.13,0:21:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1259133,1260968}Beth, Beth, look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.96,0:21:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1260968,1262595}Don't die on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.51,0:21:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1263512,1264972}I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.43,0:21:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1266432,1267933}Jo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.22,0:21:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1269226,1270186}Beth…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.57,0:21:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1280571,1284033}Beth is playing the piano\Nin her dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.29,0:21:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1299298,1301133}{\i1}Maya, great!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.13,0:21:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1301133,1302468}{\i1}Great acting!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.18,0:21:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1311185,1315648}She doesn't know the real side\Nof the acting world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.64,0:21:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1315648,1319068}Kitajima Maya, huh…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.06,0:22:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1319068,1320486}Maya, good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.48,0:22:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1320486,1321654}How do you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.65,0:22:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1321654,1322655}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.65,0:22:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1322655,1325032}I feel a little better.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.03,0:22:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1325032,1327868}Great job, Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.86,0:22:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1327868,1330204}Here's a gift from your fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.20,0:22:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1330204,1332373}It was left outside the backstage.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.38,0:22:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1339380,1340422}Purple roses?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.42,0:22:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1340422,1342258}My god, there's a card!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.25,0:22:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1342258,1347304}Let's see… "Please become\Na healthy Beth soon. —Your fan".
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.30,0:22:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1347304,1349890}Wow, an anonymous fan letter!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.89,0:22:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1350891,1355187}I'm so happy to get a gift for playing drama!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.85,0:22:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1356856,1361944}I don't know you,\Nbut thank you, Mr. Purple Rose.
Comment: 0,0:22:49.24,0:22:49.24,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:1369243,1369243}Ending
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.04,0:23:03.09,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1377042,1383090}{\blur3}It is lonely by myself…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.09,0:23:09.22,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1383090,1389221}{\blur3}…and I almost stumble.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.22,0:23:21.27,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1389221,1401275}{\blur3}Somewhere calls me here,\Njust like a whisper in the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.27,0:23:33.41,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1401275,1413412}{\blur3}Purple light, shining down\Non the horizon…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.41,0:23:39.20,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1413412,1419209}{\blur3}…more surer than words…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.20,0:23:45.42,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1419209,1425424}{\blur3}…telling us gently…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.42,0:23:51.51,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1425424,1431513}{\blur3}…that we'll meet\Neach other someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.51,0:23:57.51,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1431513,1437519}{\blur3}Of course you can\Nfly from far away…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.51,0:24:03.56,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1437519,1443567}{\blur3}…for the dream\Non my cheek…
